## Diagrams

Quarto supports creating diagrams in with Mermaid and Graphviz.


```{mermaid}
%%| echo: true

flowchart LR
  A[qmd] --> B(knitr)
  A[qmd] --> C(jupyter)
  B(knitr) --> D[md]
  C(jupyter) --> D[md]
  D[md] --> E(pandoc)
  E(pandoc) --> F(HTML)
  E(pandoc) --> G(PDF)
  E(pandoc) --> H(Word)
  E(pandoc) --> I{and more}
```
